	<article id="post-11356" class="post-11356 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-afoe">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://fistfulofeuros.net/afoe/superwahljahr-small-and-mid-sized-scandal-update/" rel="bookmark">Superwahljahr: Small and Mid-Sized Scandal Update</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://fistfulofeuros.net/afoe/superwahljahr-small-and-mid-sized-scandal-update/" title="6:01 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2021-04-25T18:01:31+00:00">April 25, 2021</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://fistfulofeuros.net/afoe/author/alex-harrowell/" title="View all posts by Alex Harrowell" rel="author">Alex Harrowell</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Just to update the German scandal outbreak:</p>
<p>In the CSU masks affair, <a href="https://www.sueddeutsche.de/bayern/maskenaffaere-sauter-csu-vermoegensarrest-1.5267903">key CSU pol Alfred Sauter&#8217;s assets have been frozen</a>.</p>
<p>The thing about health minister Jens Spahn&#8217;s villa is still going &#8211; <a href="https://m.tagesspiegel.de/politik/gute-bankverbindung-so-konnte-spahn-seine-millionenteure-berliner-villa-bezahlen/27094262.html">he got a 100% loan-to-value mortage from a local savings bank controlled by political buddies of his</a>.</p>
<p>The attendees at CSU donor&#8217;s dinners might be <a href="https://www.sueddeutsche.de/bayern/bayern-csu-affaere-spendenessen-1.5260711">named</a>.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
			
